{
  "video_id": "kJpZ1EEnlpk",
  "title": "Why Penalty Kicks Are Unfair To The Goalie",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 333.0,
      "end_time": 1470.0,
      "text": "(clock ticking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1470.0,
      "end_time": 4580.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] 0.4 seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4580.0,
      "end_time": 7210.0,
      "text": "That's the time it takes you to blink."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7210.0,
      "end_time": 9340.0,
      "text": "It's also about how long goalkeepers have"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9340.0,
      "end_time": 11240.0,
      "text": "to save a penalty kick"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11240.0,
      "end_time": 13640.0,
      "text": "or fail trying."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13640.0,
      "end_time": 15100.0,
      "text": "And it's certainly not enough time"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15100.0,
      "end_time": 17960.0,
      "text": "for a goalie to react and respond."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17960.0,
      "end_time": 21310.0,
      "text": "So goalies can't solely rely on their speed and agility"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21310.0,
      "end_time": 23680.0,
      "text": "to save a penalty kick."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23680.0,
      "end_time": 25610.0,
      "text": "Instead they have to pretty much guess"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25610.0,
      "end_time": 28544.0,
      "text": "which direction to go and rely on either luck"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 28545.0,
      "end_time": 30612.0,
      "text": "or game theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30612.0,
      "end_time": 33279.0,
      "text": "(playful music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 34680.0,
      "end_time": 37554.0,
      "text": "Game theory is a popular strategy in economics"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37554.0,
      "end_time": 40570.0,
      "text": "where the outcome of a situation relies more"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40570.0,
      "end_time": 43540.0,
      "text": "on how well you predict your opponent's actions"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43540.0,
      "end_time": 46700.0,
      "text": "than how you perform your own."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 46700.0,
      "end_time": 49630.0,
      "text": "So since the goalie has no choice but to guess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49630.0,
      "end_time": 53450.0,
      "text": "they're better off guessing logically than randomly."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 53450.0,
      "end_time": 55360.0,
      "text": "That's where economists come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 55360.0,
      "end_time": 58330.0,
      "text": "- [Ignacio] I would like to know what you do in the last"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 58330.0,
      "end_time": 60120.0,
      "text": "80 penalty kicks you faced?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60120.0,
      "end_time": 61849.0,
      "text": "Do you have any tendencies?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 61850.0,
      "end_time": 64440.0,
      "text": "What does this guy do against right-footed kickers"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 64440.0,
      "end_time": 65649.0,
      "text": "versus left-footed kickers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 65650.0,
      "end_time": 68580.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] That's economist Ignacio Palacios-Huerta."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68580.0,
      "end_time": 71429.0,
      "text": "He studied over 11,000 penalty kicks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 71430.0,
      "end_time": 75670.0,
      "text": "and in 2008 during the UEFA Champions League Final,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 75670.0,
      "end_time": 78240.0,
      "text": "it paid off, sort of."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 78240.0,
      "end_time": 80759.0,
      "text": "It was Manchester United against Chelsea."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 80760.0,
      "end_time": 83720.0,
      "text": "The game came down to a penalty shootout"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 83720.0,
      "end_time": 86350.0,
      "text": "which was the perfect opportunity for Chelsea"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 86350.0,
      "end_time": 89900.0,
      "text": "to put Huerta's advice into action."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 89100.0,
      "end_time": 90940.0,
      "text": "Along with several pointers Huerta"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 90940.0,
      "end_time": 92640.0,
      "text": "had given Chelsea's goalie"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92640.0,
      "end_time": 95600.0,
      "text": "a key insight about Manchester United"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 95600.0,
      "end_time": 97320.0,
      "text": "star Cristiano Ronaldo."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 97320.0,
      "end_time": 100639.0,
      "text": "Ronaldo would almost certainly kick the ball to the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 100640.0,
      "end_time": 102970.0,
      "text": "if he paused on the run-up."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 102970.0,
      "end_time": 104910.0,
      "text": "And the advice worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 104910.0,
      "end_time": 108110.0,
      "text": "Ronaldo indeed paused and indeed kicked the ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 108110.0,
      "end_time": 109290.0,
      "text": "to the right."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 109290.0,
      "end_time": 111820.0,
      "text": "Chelsea's goalie followed Huerta's advice"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 111820.0,
      "end_time": 113259.0,
      "text": "and made the save."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "Ultimately Manchester United won the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118100.0,
      "text": "but despite Chelsea's loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 118100.0,
      "end_time": 121460.0,
      "text": "it was clear that economists and statisticians"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 121460.0,
      "end_time": 125539.0,
      "text": "can help even the odds when it comes to penalty kicks."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 125540.0,
      "end_time": 128530.0,
      "text": "Because otherwise, it's a crap shoot for the goalie."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 128530.0,
      "end_time": 130390.0,
      "text": "In 2014 for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 130389.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134750.0,
      "text": "FiveThirtyEight calculated that 72.5% of penalties"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 134750.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "in World Cup history went in."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139510.0,
      "text": "For all competitions worldwide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 139510.0,
      "end_time": 141750.0,
      "text": "it's even higher."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 141750.0,
      "end_time": 143590.0,
      "text": "And when you take a closer look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 143590.0,
      "end_time": 144920.0,
      "text": "it's no wonder."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 144920.0,
      "end_time": 148250.0,
      "text": "Human response time takes roughly 1/10 of a second"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 148250.0,
      "end_time": 149160.0,
      "text": "to kick in."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 149160.0,
      "end_time": 152640.0,
      "text": "The average kicker kicks a 70 mile per hour ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 152640.0,
      "end_time": 154679.0,
      "text": "which means the goalie won't even register"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154680.0,
      "end_time": 158560.0,
      "text": "the ball's direction until it's about 25 feet away."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 158560.0,
      "end_time": 162270.0,
      "text": "It will take him another .5 to .7 seconds"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 162270.0,
      "end_time": 164520.0,
      "text": "to react and reach for the ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 164520.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "but by that point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 167590.0,
      "text": "it's all over."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167590.0,
      "end_time": 169580.0,
      "text": "Now the goalie can improve the odds"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169580.0,
      "end_time": 173120.0,
      "text": "if they start to move before the ball is even kicked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 173120.0,
      "end_time": 175800.0,
      "text": "but the goalie still has to basically guess a side"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 175800.0,
      "end_time": 177500.0,
      "text": "and just go for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 177500.0,
      "end_time": 179463.0,
      "text": "So if time is the goalie's enemy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179463.0,
      "end_time": 183459.0,
      "text": "maybe we should just move the penalty kicker further back."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183460.0,
      "end_time": 186470.0,
      "text": "But for now, economists are a goalie's best friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 186470.0,
      "end_time": 188850.0,
      "text": "when it comes to stopping penalty kicks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 188850.0,
      "end_time": 191640.0,
      "text": "and turns out, Huerta is helping a team"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191640.0,
      "end_time": 194220.0,
      "text": "in the 2018 World Cup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 194220.0,
      "end_time": 195810.0,
      "text": "though he wouldn't tell us who."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 195810.0,
      "end_time": 198477.0,
      "text": "(playful music)"
    }
  ]
}